dc_title_s: Land Use (Existing and Future) Monroe County, WI 2010
dc_description_s: These data layers represent land use for Monroe County, Wisconsin at 2010. It is a feature class within the geodatabase 'Monroe_LandUse_2010.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Monroe_Existing_LandUse_2010', and 'Monroe_Future_LandUse_2010'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
